IMMEDIATE
No.55/4/CF-62
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 4th May 1962.
The undersigned is directed to inform the Members
of the Council of Ministers that Shri R.M. Hajarnavis assumed the
office of Deputy Minister in the Ministry of Mines & Fuel wi th
effect from the afternoon of Thursday, May 3, 1962.
Shri R.M.
Hajarnavis continues to be Deputy Minister in the Ministry of
Law also, until other arrang ements are made.
( B.G. Rau )
Joint Secretary to the Cabinet.
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Principal Private Secretary to the
Prime Minister/the Private Secretary to the Prime Minister,
for information.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the President/the
Private Secretary to the Vice-President, for information.
Belan
( B.G. Rau )
Joint Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy forward ed to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/
Additional Secretaries to the Government of India/the Chairman,
Railway Board, for information.
Copy forwarded to alll Ministries of the Government of
India/Depar tment of Parliamentary Affairs/Planning Commission/
Department of Atomic Energy/Prime Minister's Secretariat/
Lok Sabha Secretariat/Rajya Sabha Secretariat, for info rmation.
( D.P. Chopra )
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
*P.C*
350 copies.
